# Dataset: Food Delivery Time Prediction Case Study.xlsx

## Business Purpose
This dataset represents operational delivery intelligence for food delivery services. It is primarily used for delivery SLA monitoring, rider performance analysis, operational efficiency tracking, and logistics optimization.

---

## Dataset Category
Operational / Delivery Intelligence Dataset

---

## Key Business Entities
- Delivery Partners
- Delivery Operations
- Restaurants
- Delivery Locations
- Vehicle Types

---

## Key Columns

| Column Name | Description |
|---|---|
| ID | Unique delivery transaction identifier |
| Delivery_person_ID | Unique delivery partner identifier |
| Delivery_person_Age | Age of delivery partner |
| Delivery_person_Ratings | Delivery partner performance rating |
| Restaurant_latitude | Restaurant latitude coordinate |
| Restaurant_longitude | Restaurant longitude coordinate |
| Delivery_location_latitude | Customer delivery latitude |
| Delivery_location_longitude | Customer delivery longitude |
| Type_of_order | Order category |
| Type_of_vehicle | Vehicle used for delivery |
| Time_taken(min) | Total delivery duration |

---

## Potential KPIs
- Average Delivery Time
- Delivery SLA Compliance %
- Delivery Partner Performance Rating
- Orders by Vehicle Type
- Fastest vs Slowest Delivery Zones
- Average Delivery Time by Order Type
- Rider Efficiency Metrics
- Delivery Trend Analysis

---

## Business Use Cases
- Delivery SLA monitoring
- Rider performance analysis
- Logistics optimization
- Operational efficiency tracking
- Delivery zone analysis
- Vehicle utilization analytics
- Peak delivery performance monitoring

---

## Expected Target Tables

### Fact Tables
- fact_deliveries

### Dimension Tables
- dim_delivery_partner
- dim_location
- dim_vehicle
- dim_order_type
- dim_restaurant

